{"tid":89655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【47秒跳69蚊】強國古惑咪錶 的士客：跳快過我個心","createTime":"2017-01-21T13:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T13:17:11.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a053fcf16aba8ba1b87a919e9a5382ff459c44d","tid":89655,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170121&amp;guid=56203218&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170121%26guid%3D56203218%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=lmhI%2F5UZH7%2FTQnJvND34gH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=05f3aa74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170121%26guid%3D56203218%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=34f9e30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170121&amp;guid=56203218&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n在內地坐的士，遇到司機亂開價、不按咪錶收費當然驚，要是咪錶不規則跳動，這可能更驚！一名網民在吉林長春坐的士，拍下咪錶在47秒內急跳69元（人民幣．下同），嚇得大嗌要下車，事件已經引發當局關注，聲稱已經開始調查。<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，司機與坐在前座的男子在交談，鏡頭前的咪錶不斷的跳，從開始的28元，一直跳到97元，乘客一直向司機質疑咪錶是否有問題，稱「比我心跳得都快啊」，但司機卻稱「你打哪個車都這樣」。<br />\n<br />\n從兩人說話速度、車窗外景物的速度，片段都未有剪接過，網民估計的士車速不會超過每小時80公里。<br />\n<br />\n當地的政府部門稱目前仍未接到有人投訴，但已經開始查事件，更稱要是發現有人惡意修改咪錶，最高可罰款5,000元。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/211708_21284d11a1f89a9654036667e465d09b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F211708_21284d11a1f89a9654036667e465d09b.jpg&h=c869a901&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}